<p>Is there way to check if existing established connection on port? I wanna check if anyone connected to me through VNC. I've tried to write following method:</p>  <pre><code>    private static bool IsInUse(int port)     {         IPGlobalProperties ipGlobalProperties = IPGlobalProperties.GetIPGlobalProperties();         TcpConnectionInformation[] tcpConnInfoArray = ipGlobalProperties.GetActiveTcpConnections();          var c = tcpConnInfoArray.FirstOrDefault(r =&gt; r.LocalEndPoint.Port == 5900);         if (c != null)         {             return c.RemoteEndPoint.Address != null;         }         return false;     } </code></pre>  <p>but it doesn't work in some cases.</p>